3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of birds, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">peck</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:609b:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">609b5</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ ἁλιάετος . . τὰ λιμναῖα κ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">preys</tr_> on the lagoon life, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:593b:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">593b24</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σπειρὴν κ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">peck</tr_> at, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:449\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">449</biblScope> </bibl>; of fish, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">gnaw</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:620b:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">620b17</biblScope> </bibl>; of a snake, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">strike</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12:204\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.204</biblScope> </bibl>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, of wood or seeds, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be worm-eaten</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:3:18:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"